name: Clearstar OpenEden USDC
description: Clearstar Labs is an onchain infrastructure provider and strategy generation powerhouse. We advice a multibillion EUR manager in Switzerland and launch our on prop onchain strategies. This one is simple a Morpho Vault we curate on Base in partnership with OpenEden. Morpho Vaults are curated lending vaults that can allocate deposits to any number of Morpho Markets. Each vault is customizable and has a different risk profile. Curators are independent, third-party risk experts who use their expertise to offer various Morpho Vaults.
